parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become unable to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls
the transmission warning light illuminates
the vehicle is unable to shift into gear
the vehicle jerks or lurches when shifting
the transmission fluid leaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The slipping of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or jerk when shifting, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.

the vehicle loses power
the transmission warning light illuminates
the vehicle jerks or lurches when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The leaking of transmission fluid can cause the transmission to fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

the transmission warning light illuminates

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion and rusting of the frame can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded. The rusting of the frame can also cause the rear traction control bar to break loose, leading to loss of control and potential accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may exhibit unusual noises
such as creaking or grinding sounds
while driving. The steering wheel may pull to one side
and the vehicle may vibrate or shake. In severe cases
the frame may rust to the point where it breaks
causing the vehicle to lose control or become undrivable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear traction control bar can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle may exhibit unusual noises
such as creaking or grinding sounds
while driving. The steering wheel may pull to one side
and the vehicle may vibrate or shake. In severe cases
the rear traction control bar may break loose
causing the vehicle to lose control or become undrivable.
